{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"946fc9d93d","title":"杨成武传达陈伯达江青关于萧华问题的指示","origin":"1967年3月北京玻璃总厂红卫兵联络站编《中央首长讲话（1）》","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e74dee0a8a","index":0,"year":1967,"month":1,"day":20,"articleId":"946fc9d93d"}],"tags":[{"id":"06af9ed14a","name":"肖华","type":"人物"},{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"82305e518c","name":"江青","type":"人物"},{"id":"e1397e909a","name":"杨成武","type":"人物"},{"id":"e46e45351b","name":"陈伯达","type":"人物"},{"id":"ef71f03227","name":"中央文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"421124ccd3","name":"江青"},{"id":"48606ca4e5","name":"陈伯达"},{"id":"53bbb63fc8","name":"杨成武"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b14496336d","type":"title","text":"杨成武传达陈伯达江青关于肖华问题的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"946fc9d93d"},{"id":"3088caa3c2","type":"authors","text":"杨成武陈伯达江青","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"946fc9d93d"},{"id":"ead334bf5a","type":"paragraph","text":"一、传达和记录一律收回烧毁。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"946fc9d93d"},{"id":"370f8c45f7","type":"paragraph","text":"二、凡是贴在墙上的大字报、传单都盖起来。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"946fc9d93d"},{"id":"be898f91dc","type":"paragraph","text":"三、肖华同志的大字报不准上街，因为他是总政主任，有国际影响，中央未定性质。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"946fc9d93d"},{"id":"0aa4128dec","type":"paragraph","text":"四、向外传达了的，告诉他们不要相信。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"946fc9d93d"},{"id":"6027fcc395","type":"paragraph","text":"五、中央文革、办事处准备发声明，对陈伯达、江青同志的讲话有很大的歪曲和造谣，传到那里，从那里追回。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"946fc9d93d"}],"page":{"id":"d6678b31ec","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"946fc9d93d","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}